 "remarks": "Central A/C system. 3 BR, 2 BA townhouse-style unit where all three levels are loaded with charm and character. Features include a Mansard roof (tall ceilings on 2nd floor), wide plank flooring, hand hewn beams, multiple fireplaces, newer kitchen with stainless steel appliances and washer dryer in unit. French doors lead to bluestone patio overlooking large, private backyard with plenty of level play area. Located in award-winning Hindley School district. Walk to train, schools, beaches, shopping. Convenient to I-95 and ideal commute to Stamford or NYC. House is currently fully furnished. Unfurnished is possible with 1+ year lease. Close to Noroton Heights Train, beaches, shops, exercise, YMCA, Equinox, and Whole Foods. 1 Dog considered. Right side of 2 Family house on nearly 1/2 acre. Central A/C",
